           move      rr-cod-lst           to   d-prz-ven-cod-lst      .
           move      rf-dcp-prz-lst       to   d-prz-ven-prz-lsb      .
           move      c-sgl                to   d-prz-ven-sgl-vlb      .
           move      c-dec                to   d-prz-ven-dec-vlb      .
           move      spaces               to   d-prz-ven-tfu-prz      .
           move      rr-dat-exp           to   d-prz-ven-dat-rfp      .
           move      zero                 to   d-prz-ven-qta-rif      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Richiamo del sottoprogramma                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   det-prz-ven-cll-000  thru det-prz-ven-cll-999    .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
