           move      rf-dcp-per-scr (4)   to   d-per-scr-psr-pro (4)  .
           move      rf-dcp-per-scr (5)   to   d-per-scr-psr-pro (5)  .
           move      zero                 to   d-per-scr-csr-pro      .
           move      zero                 to   d-per-scr-psr-cli (1)  .
           move      zero                 to   d-per-scr-psr-cli (2)  .
