      *                      * Flag di uscita ad errore                *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   w-let-arc-zls-flg      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Descrizione listino                     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      all   "."            to   w-let-arc-zls-des      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Valuta per il listino                   *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-let-arc-zls-vlt      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Uscita                                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     let-arc-zls-999.
       let-arc-zls-999.
           exit.

